            "heading": "Early Beginnings",
            "content": "<p>Sarah was getting headaches from store bought candles. She started making soy wax candles on their stove. The first one made solved the problem of the migraines she was getting from petroleum chemicals found in many candles. They launched an Etsy shop and shortly after hired their first employee.</p>"
